# 5️⃣ Cloud Service Models

Very common interview question.

---

## IaaS (Infrastructure as a Service)

You rent:

* servers
* storage
* networking

You manage OS and applications.

---

### Example

[Amazon EC2](https://aws.amazon.com/ec2/?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

---

### Mental Model

Rent empty apartment.

You furnish everything.

---

## PaaS (Platform as a Service)

You deploy code.

Provider manages infrastructure.

---

### Examples

[Google App Engine](https://cloud.google.com/appengine?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

---

### Mental Model

Fully furnished apartment.

Just move in.

---

## SaaS (Software as a Service)

Ready-made software.

---

### Examples

[Gmail](https://mail.google.com?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

[Google Docs](https://docs.google.com?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

---

### Mental Model

Hotel room.

Use directly.

---

# Easy Comparison

| Model | Manage Yourself |
| ----- | --------------- |
| IaaS  | Most            |
| PaaS  | Less            |
| SaaS  | Almost nothing  |

